Package org.eclipse.egf.common.ui.field

Class Summary
ContextElementFieldEditor Implements a field editor that allows the end-user to enter a context element value.
DomainFieldEditor Implements a field editor that allows the end-user to select an IFile used as domain.
JavaClassFieldEditor Implements a field editor that allows the end-user to select a Java type.
JavaScopeClassFieldEditor Implements a field editor that allows the end-user to select a Java type.
LabelFieldEditor A field editor to display labels not associated with other widgets.
SpacerFieldEditor A field editor used as a separator in a preference page.
ValidatingStringButtonFieldEditor Implement a string button field editor that delegated its validation to an IValidator object if provided.
WorkspaceFileFieldEditor Implements a field editor that allows the end-user to select an IFile in the workspace.
